Ayahku akan penuhi maumu.

359
00:31:55,831 --> 00:31:56,915
Siapa ayahmu?

360
00:31:56,998 --> 00:31:58,041
Kapten Morgan.

361
00:31:58,792 --> 00:32:00,419
Komandan pangkalan Marinir.

362
00:32:02,379 --> 00:32:03,839
